      "text": [
        " اَلْأُضْحِيَّةِ يُكْسَرُ قَرْنُهَا قَالَ «إِذَا كَانَ اَلْقَرْنُ اَلدَّاخِلُ صَحِيحاً فَهِيَ تُجْزِي »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3062 - Jameel narrated from Abu Abdullah (as) regarding a sacrificial animal whose horn is broken.\nImam (as) said: \"If the inner horn is intact, it suffices.\""
        ]
      }
